data.description:
One assigned garage space included. Electricity, & Water included! 

Come view this spacious, beautiful 1 Bedroom riverside condo in Southwest DC! This comfortable unit features over-sized windows flooding the unit with sunlight. The kitchen features deep drawers, birch wood cabinets, a dishwasher, some stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops.

Community amenities include an on-site fitness center 24/7 front desk service. Adjacent to the river, the fenced-in pool and patio area provide the perfect secluded place to relax on a beautiful summer day. Shared laundry, bike storage, and parking are available in the basement of the building.

Optimally located to enjoy the best of Waterfront. This condo is conveniently located close to the SW Wharf with plenty of restaurants and entertainment. Just 3 blocks away from Waterfront Metro station, 1 block away from Southwest Waterfront Park, and a few blocks away from National Park Stadium, Audi Field, Dinner Cruise Ships, Arena Stage, and Safeway Grocery Store

This will not stay in the market for long! Come schedule a viewing today!

Electricity & Water included. Internet/cable can be included in the rent - tenant is not allowed to make any changes to the package or else they assume the total cost.

1435 4th St SW #B107
